OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA wet start for many, then
OL,6,Fbrighter with scattered heavy and
OL,7,Flocally thundery showers. Cool and
OL,8,Fblustery with strong winds, especially
OL,9,Fnear Irish Sea coasts and over the
OL,10,Fhills. Feeling warmer when the
OL,11,Fsunshine comes out though.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FShowers becoming less
OL,14,Ffrequent this evening and overnight,
OL,15,Fwith some clear spells developing
OL,16,Facross the country later in the night.
OL,17,FWinds slowly easing.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
