OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FMuch drier on Friday, though
OL,6,Fshowers are still likely in places.
OL,7,FVariable amounts of cloud with bright
OL,8,For sunny spells for many. Feeling cool
OL,9,Ffor the time of year.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FWindy
OL,12,Fat first on Saturday with overnight
OL,13,Frain clearing to brighter skies later.
OL,14,FSunshine and showers on Sunday.
OL,15,FFurther rain Sunday night, ahead of a
OL,16,Fbrighter, showery day on Monday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
